Class AgentMovementData

  • java.lang.Object
    • Statistics.AgentMovementData
  • public class AgentMovementData
extends java.lang.Object
    AgentMovementData class keeps data about Agent movement, List agentMovement - keeps data for each millisecond of movement (agentMovement.size() == number of milliseconds)

        Creates collection of SpaceTimeData objects for each millisecond of movement
        Parameters:
        x1 - x coordinate of starting point
        y1 - y coordinate of starting point
        x2 - x coordinate of finish point
        y2 - y coordinate of finish point
        startTime - time of beginning of movement
        finishTime - time of ending of movement
        lastMovement - if it is the last movement we should include the last point in SpaceTimeData collection
